Start a local Apache Kafka instance.

Usage:
  confluent local kafka start [flags]

Flags:
      --kafka-rest-port string    Kafka REST port number. (default "8082")
      --plaintext-ports strings   A comma-separated list of port numbers for plaintext producer and consumer clients for brokers. If not specified, random free ports will be used.
      --num-brokers int32         Number of brokers (between 1 and 4, inclusive) in the Confluent Local Kafka cluster. (default 1)

Global Flags:
  -h, --help            Show help for this command.
      --unsafe-trace    Equivalent to -vvvv, but also log HTTP requests and responses which might contain plaintext secrets.
  -v, --verbose count   Increase verbosity (-v for warn, -vv for info, -vvv for debug, -vvvv for trace).
